{"tid":1229561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想輕生嗰班同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:50:36.000Z","uid":108668,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce409140f50630436df28b75da4eae1840ab5c0f","tid":1229561,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:28:52.000Z","msg":"尋晚大家都應該知發生咩事<br />\n雖然已經挽回唔到<br />\n但希望各位唔好仿效呢個做法<br />\n香港需要你地<br />\n你地咁做只會令我地失去多一個戰友<br />\n令更多同路人傷心<br />\n唔止你地 尋晚到而家只要見到呢件事我都係忍唔住流眼淚 真係好心痛<br />\n<br />\n希望你地唔好咁做 唔好再話自己都想死 清醒啲！！！！！<br />\n留返條命同我地一齊保住自由嘅香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊長命百歲身體健康睇住淋病閱哦同黑警仆街陷家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄺仔因為呢件事已經瀕臨崩潰<br />\n佢連日來為我地 為香港做咗咁多嘢<br />\n你地係咪想佢真係精神崩潰呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不受傷 不流血！！！！<br />\n抗爭到底！！！<br />\n今日維園見！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNO2TEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNO2TEb.jpg&h=d2297826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"528f8e5ca4116c5fa7dc6a18bf531d242a8957fa","tid":1229561,"uid":108668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87b7cb6f94d1e063c47d6e6172f5134f987c1863","tid":1229561,"uid":108668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d22a26d653ccd43f30ef4e31a62c664937b5cd87","tid":1229561,"uid":108668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a16ff387e1a7bfc60684bf6e09190665c41aa0ce","tid":1229561,"uid":108668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bede8815cf3b2b37529770e1e6e9f9eb23a4d3c9","tid":